---
title: Lemony Crusted Chicken Breasts with Dill Dressing and Sweet Potatoes
description: Coat tender chicken breasts with a zesty crumb, for a dinner that's sure to please. With sweet potato wedges, fresh salad, a tangy mustard dressing, and a creamy dill sauce for dipping, this meal is the best of the best!
